---
title: Roasted Cauliflower Bengali Curry with Basmati Rice and Herbs
description: Curry on rice is all well and good, but when the Bengali curry paste meets coconut milk to make a sensational curry, now that’s
magical. Studded with refreshing herbs and roasted cauliflower, this dish packs flavour in every bite.

